  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1481310/extras/95cdcc9976f689d7bdb052927d103110.avif?t=1773677882\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1481310/extras_big/95cdcc9976f689d7bdb052927d103110.avif?t=1773677882 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TeamJumpers: New Reality, is a complete remake/remaster of an old indie game made back in 2018. The focus on this one is interdimensional travel. Throughout your journey You will be discovering <i>new realities</i> with challenging bosses<i>, a simple yet fun combat system, and secrets to be revealed, this world is yours to explore! </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   • Traverse New realities by yourself, or with a friend if you'd like!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   • Both players have their own unique ability! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   • Explore across different bosses and uncover the secrets of the multiverse!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   • Fight a variety of different enemies across 3 different dimensions and make your way to the end to fight 'the one pulling the strings'</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1481310/extras/95cdcc9976f689d7bdb052927d103110.avif?t=1773677882\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1481310/extras_big/95cdcc9976f689d7bdb052927d103110.avif?t=1773677882 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >TeamJumpers: New Reality, is a complete remake/remaster of an old indie game made back in 2018. The focus on this one is interdimensional travel. Throughout your journey You will be discovering <i>new realities</i> with challenging bosses<i>, a simple yet fun combat system, and secrets to be revealed, this world is yours to explore! </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   • Traverse New realities by yourself, or with a friend if you'd like!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   • Both players have their own unique ability! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   • Explore across different bosses and uncover the secrets of the multiverse!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   • Fight a variety of different enemies across 3 different dimensions and make your way to the end to fight 'the one pulling the strings'</p>",
